These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Job: chef, dancer, social-worker, lawyer
House: ranch-style, wooden, townhouse, cape-cod
1. Job:chef is on the right of House:townhouse##1
2. House:cape-cod is on the far left##1
3. House:townhouse is between House:wooden and Job:dancer##2
4. Job:lawyer is on the far left##1
5. Job:social-worker is between Job:dancer and Job:chef##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Job   | lawyer         | dancer   | social-worker | chef       |
| House      | cape-cod | ranch-style | townhouse   | wooden |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Sport: baseball, snowboarding, cycling, handball
Beverage: coffee, milk, sprite, fanta
1. Beverage:fanta is between Sport:cycling and Beverage:milk##2
2. Sport:handball is on the far right##1
3. Beverage:sprite is on the right of Beverage:coffee##1
4. Sport:baseball is on the left of Beverage:coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Sport         | snowboarding | baseball | cycling | handball |
| Beverage   | milk    | fanta   | coffee | sprite       |

